Introducing the New
Boeing 737-300!
We Make Flying Easy

Introducing the Automated AirFair
Now AirCal Makes the AirFair Frequent Traveler Program Easier...
Finally, a frequent traveler program with nothing
for you to do but decide where you'll be spend-
ing your next vacation!
That's right! No confusing forms to fill out, and
no more keeping track of old receipts. AirCal's
new Air Fair has been completely automated
for your convenience! Now you can avoid
keeping track of all those past flights, because
we'll do it all for you!
BEGINNING JANUARY 1, 1985, everytime you
fly with us you can be accumulating mileage
towards free trips and exciting vacations. You
can start earning free flights on AirCal after
only 10,000 miles! Plus, we make it easy to reach
an award level quick, because after you've
enrolled with us, we'll put 3000 bonus miles
in your account automatically. Have your trave
agent fill out the special Travel Agent section,
and you can even gain an extra 1000 enroll-
ment miles!
EASY TO USE
The ease of our new program can be found
in the personalized AirFair
membership card.
AIRCAL
AIREAR
Frequent Traveler Program
MR.
JOHN SMITH
1234567
Once
you receive your
AirFair card and per-
sonalized account number, simply identity your-
self as an AirFair member each time you make
a reservation with us, and give your number to
our sales agent.
Then, when you check-in for your flight, show
our agent your AirFair card.
We do the rest!
Your mileage is automatically tracked by our
computers and you are sent a statement after
each month that you fly with us. Then you can
decide whether you want to redeem at that
time, or keep building your account for even
bigger awards!
EASY TO EARN
We'll also send you information on how you
can take advantage of special bonus opportu-
nities to earn "Easy Miles." Throughout the
program we will extend these incredible bonus
mile offers for flying certain flights, or between
selected cities. These miles are added to your
regular miles, and make it even easier to win
AirFair awards
EASY TO WIN
Since we keep track of your mileage, you'll
never have to worry about when you'll have
enough mileage for an AirFair award. And
we have some of the greatest travel awards
anywhere. Exciting trips to destinations through-
out the West; fun vacations in Los Angeles,
San Francisco; resort adventures in Palm Springs
and Lake Tahoe; free Avis rental cars, and
much, much more...
Ask a participating travel agent or an AirCal
Representative for an enrollment form and join
the new AirFair program. Then you can start
putting your miles with us to good use!
The new AirCal AirFair. It's just what you'd expect
from the airline that makes flying easy.
AIRCAL
AirCal AirFair, P.O. Box Z, Newport Beach, CA 92658-8913
